	——— „Symbolism of the Dome“. — _Indian Historical Quarterly_, vol. 14 (March 1938).
	Coomaraswamy, L. „The Perilous Bridge of Welfare“. — _Harvard Journal of Asiatic Studies_, vol. 8 (1944). (By Dona Luisa Coomaraswamy, wife of Ananda Coomaraswamy, cited as D. L. Coomaraswamy.)
